item.title: CVE-2017-2143|2024-08-05T13:48:03.502Z -- frogman%20office%20inc. -- cs-cart%20japanese%20edition
item.description: CS-Cart Japanese Edition v4.3.10-jp-1 and earlier, CS-Cart Multivendor Japanese Edition v4.3.10-jp-1 and earlier allows remote attackers to bypass access restriction to create a request to return a customer purchased item via rma.post.php.

item.title: CVE-2017-2138|2024-08-05T13:39:32.358Z -- frogman%20office%20inc. -- cs-cart%20japanese%20edition
item.description: Cross-site request forgery (CSRF) vulnerability in CS-Cart Japanese Edition v4.3.10 and earlier (excluding v2 and v3), CS-Cart Multivendor Japanese Edition v4.3.10 and earlier (excluding v2 and v3) allows remote attackers to hijack the authentication of administrators via unspecified vectors.

item.title: CVE-2017-10886|2024-08-05T17:50:12.728Z -- frogman%20office%20inc. -- cs-cart%20japanese%20edition

item.title: CVE-2017-2139|2024-08-05T13:39:32.360Z -- frogman%20office%20inc. -- cs-cart%20japanese%20edition
item.description: CS-Cart Japanese Edition v4.3.10 and earlier (excluding v2 and v3), CS-Cart Multivendor Japanese Edition v4.3.10 and earlier (excluding v2 and v3) allows remote attackers to bypass access restriction to obtain customer information via orders.pre.php.
